    <img class="w-full h-full rounded-lg z-10" src={img} alt="">
  </header>

  <article class="bg-boldsea2 w-full h-[120px] p-[20px] rounded-es-lg rounded-ee-lg absolute bottom-0 z-[-1]">
    <div>
      <h1 class="text-fontblue font-bold text-[24px]">{title}</h1>
    </div>
    <div>
      <p class="text-fontbluelight">Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Dignissimos odio odit iste aliquid obcaecati mollitia sequi cupiditate magni et amet perferendis laborum at eius repellendus reiciendis, omnis reprehenderit molestias incidunt?</p>
    </div>
  </article>
</section>